Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) is one of the world's largest multinational information technology (IT) services, consulting, and business solutions companies. It was founded by Jamsetji Tata in 1968 as a division of Tata Sons Limited. TCS provides services to various industries such as banking, finance, insurance, retail, telecommunications, manufacturing, energy, utilities, and healthcare.

TCS offers a wide range of solutions including digital transformation, cloud, artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning (ML), cybersecurity, automation, and analytics. The company has a strong focus on innovation and investing in R&D, with centers across the globe dedicated to emerging technologies.

For developers and data scientists, TCS provides platforms like Ignio (AI-powered automation platform) and Xylem (a comprehensive AI solution for businesses). These tools can help streamline processes, make predictions, and optimize business operations using machine learning algorithms.
